{"TopicId":210902,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"The orbit gradient is broken","CreatedByName":"Kanzler_Jif","CreatedById":224059,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-02T15:37:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kanzler_Jif","CreatedById":224059,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-02T15:37:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello everybody!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn the map, my ship is moving against the gradient of the orbit. Previously, the gradient was behind. Maneuvers and trajectories work fine. The problem is not serious, but it is unpleasant to the eyes. No mods. Version 1.12.4. win64.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002220221202175802-1.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002269.00\u0022 height=\u0022662\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/mTVMt60/20221202175802-1.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"18Watt","CreatedById":198538,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-02T17:28:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is configurable in the settings. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnder settings, select the \u0027Graphics\u0027 tab.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe item you want is called \u0027Orbit Line Fade Reversed\u0027. \u00A0Click the radio button to un-select it. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kanzler_Jif","CreatedById":224059,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-02T19:55:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224205056\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022210902\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221670002107\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022198538\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u002218Watt\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, 18Watt said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is configurable in the settings. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnder settings, select the \u0027Graphics\u0027 tab.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe item you want is called \u0027Orbit Line Fade Reversed\u0027. \u00A0Click the radio button to un-select it. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt worked. Thanks!\u003Cbr\u003E\nNow I wonder how I could accidentally change it in the game...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"18Watt","CreatedById":198538,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-02T19:58:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224205110\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022210902\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221670010909\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022224059\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kanzler_Jif\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Kanzler_Jif said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt worked. Thanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re welcome. \u00A0Also, I forgot to say, \u0022Welcome to the KSP forums \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/224059-kanzler_jif/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022224059\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/224059-kanzler_jif/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kanzler_Jif\u003C/a\u003E!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224205110\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022210902\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221670010909\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022224059\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kanzler_Jif\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Kanzler_Jif said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow I wonder how I could accidentally change it in the game...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHard telling. \u00A0When that happens to me I just blame it on elves or ghosts that mess up my settings while I\u0027m not looking. \u00A0Because I know it wasn\u0027t me. \u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}